text: Hjalmar Saxtorph (19 April 1883 - 24 April 1942) was a Danish swimmer. He competed at the 1906 Intercalated Games and the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:1942 deaths Category:Danish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Denmark Category:Swimmers at the 1906 Intercalated Games Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics
